# Trivy ignore list - CVEs we have triaged and accepted
#
# Format: one CVE ID per line. Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# Only add a CVE here AFTER:
#   1. Reading the upstream advisory
#   2. Confirming the vulnerable code path is NOT exercised in our app
#   3. Recording a decision (with date + reason) below
#
# Example:
#   # Accepted 2026-05-23 - vulnerable function not called in our code paths
#   CVE-2024-XXXXX
